data.meta_description:
Raquel Torres married to Stephen Ames aboard a liner .
Raquel Torres , the Mexican screen actress , and Stephen Ames , former husband of Adrienne Ames , were married aboard the liner Lurline in Los Angeles harbour . After the ceremony the couple sailed aboard the same ship for a honeymoon in Honolulu .
Photo shows , Raquel Torres and Stephen Ames after their wedding . 
2 May 1934
